title: Mayor dismisses claims that rates will fall in merged councils (Ku-ring-gai Council)
text: ( Source : Ku-ring-gai Council ) New Ku-ring-gai Mayor Cheryl Szatow has refuted a state government report that ratepayers will be better off if council mergers proceed. The NSW Office of Local Government released the report earlier this week
